quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  71,1,"Men imminii Nuuhu haa e yim…ìe makko …ìen, fii noddugol …ìe jertina …ìe, ado lette muusu…óe arde e ma…ì…ìe, sabu ko …ìe woni e sirkannde kon Allah."
  71,2,"Nuuhu maakani yim…ìe makko …ìen : ko onon yo yim…ìe am, min ko mi jertinoowo on, …ìanngin…óo jertinaango lette habbitii…ói on, si tawii on tuubanaali Allah."
  71,3,"Jertinaango am ngon, ko wi'ugol on : rewee Allah tun, hara on kafidaali Mo e go…ó…óum goo, huliron Mo …óoftagol yamiraa…ói Makko e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko, …óofto…óon lam e ko mi yamirta on kon."
  71,4,"Si on wa…óii …óum, Allah haforanany on junuubi mon …ói humondiraa…ói e haqqeeji jeyaa…ìe …ìen, O juutina laje mofte mon …óen haa e happu mo Allah anndi, nguurnon leydi fotde hi…óon √±ii…ìi e …óum. Ko woni tun, maayde nden si hewtii, ngal nennetaake, si …óon anndunoo …óum, on tii…ónorayno gom…óingol Allah, tuubun e sirku e majjere ko won…óon e mun."
  71,5,"Nuuhu maaki : Joomi am, mi jokkindirii noddirgol yim…ìe am …ìen e rewugol Ma e wootin…óine, jemma e √±alorma ko ewindii."
  71,6,"Kono noddaandu am ndun …ìeydaani …ìe, si wanaa dogugol w…ó…óitoo ko mi noddata …ìe e mun kon."
  71,7,"Tuma kala kadi nde mi noddi …ìe e ko …ìe haforantee junuubi : wano rewugol Ma An tun, …óofto Maa An e Nulaa…óo Maa on, …ìe uddira noppi ma…ì…ìe …óin kollin …óin fii wata …ìe nanu, …ìe buumora comci ma…ì…ìe …óin fii wata …ìe yi'am, …ìe duumii e sirkugol ngol, …ìe townitanii ja…ìugol noddaandu am ndun, mawnintinanoo ndu."
  71,8,"Refti Joomi am, mi noddirii …ìee e kene."
  71,9,"Refti mi townanii …ìe hito ka noddugol, mi gunndii …ìe gunndagol, mi noddiri …ìe noone fow."
  71,10,"Mi wi*ani …ìe : ko onon yo yim…ìe am, …óa…ì…ìiree Joomi mon tuubaneede, tawde O siforii wonnde Haforoowo junuubi kala tuubu…óo e jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  71,11,"Si on wa…óii …óum, Allah jippiniray to…ìo ngon e moo…óon, jokkondiral tuma haaju mon yani e maggo, hara on he…ìataa kokke."
  71,12,"O ye…óay on jawle e …ìi…ó…ìe …óuu…óu…ìe, O wa…óana on gese …óe √±aamoton dim…óe mun, O wa…óana on can…ói ka yaron yarnon gese e neemoraa…ói mon."
  71,13,"E ko he…ìi on yim…ìe am, on hulataa manngural Allah ngal, hi…óon yeddiral Mo yawitaare?"
  71,14,"Gom…óii le O tagirii on sagara-sagara, immorde e maniyyu, hooti he…ó…óere, hooti huyre."
  71,15,"E on yi'aali no Allah tagiri kammuuli jee…ói…ói tegondir…ói, kammu kala ina e hoore nguya?"
  71,16,"O wa…ói lewru ndun ka kammu aduna, ina heen ndaygu yim…ìe leydi ndin; O wa…ói naange ngen kadi ndayginnge."
  71,17,"Ko Allah tagiri e leydi ndin e tagugol baaba mon Aadama e mayri, hooti ko e mayri wuurdaton ko ndi funnata."
  71,18,"Refti O ruttiray on e mayri …ìaawo on maayude, O yaltinira ummintineede e mayre yaltudee."
  71,19,"Allah wa…óiranii on leydi ndin weertaandi hebliraandi ka ho…óee."
  71,20,"Fii no naatiron e mayri laawi yaaju…ói, ka …óa…ì…ìiron arsike dagii…óo."
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : Joomi am, yim…ìe am …ìen salanike lam e ko mi yamiri …ìe wootin…óingol Ma rewa Maa kon An tun. Jaasu…ìe …ìen e ma…ì…ìe jokki hooree…ìe …ìe neeminir…óaa …ìen e ma…ì…ìe jawle e …ìi…ó…ìe. Hara le kon ko neeminir…óaa …ìe …ìeydaali …ìe si wanaa majjere."
  71,22,"Hooree…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen fewji feere mawnde, fii no …ìe cuynira jaasu…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen e Nuuhu."
  71,23,"∆Åe wi'ani jokku…ìe …ìen : wata on terto dey rewetee…ói mon …óin : wata on terto rewugol sanamuuji mon …óin Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqhta, e Nasr."
  71,24,"Ko pellet, …ìe majjinirii yim…ìe …óuu…óu…ìe, …óii sanamuuji ma…ì…ìe. Joomi, wata A …ìeydir too√±ir…ìe ko'e mun …ìen geddi e keeferaaku, si wanaa majjugol goonga."
  71,25,"Ko sabu goopi ma…ì…ìe …ói …ìe faggitinoo …óin, …ìe yoliranoo waame …óen, …ìe naadoyaa kisan ka Yiite …ìaawo maayde ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe he…ìanaano ko'e ma…ì…ìe ko wanaa Allah, dan…óndoowo …ìe yoolagol e sumgol."
  71,26,"Nde Allah humpitunoo Nuuhu wonnde hay gooto gom…óintaa e yim…ìe maa …ìen si wanaa …ìeya gom…óinnoo…ìe, O maaki kadi: Joomi am, wata A accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeere gooto yiilatoo…óo wollo dilloowo."
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si A nennanii …ìe An Joomi amen, …ìe majjinoyay jeyaa…ìe Maa gom…óim…ìe …ìen, …ìe jiidoytaako kadi si wanaa bonnoo…ìe …ìe …óoftotaako Ma, tii…óu…ìe yeddugol …ìe yettatah neemaaji Maa …óin."
  71,28,"Joomi am, haforanam junuubi am, min e jibim…ìe lam …ìen, haforanaa kala gom…óin…óo naatu…óo ka suudu am, e gom…óim…ìe wor…ìe …ìen e gom…óim…ìe rew…ìe …ìen; wata A …ìeydir too√±ir…ìe ko'e mun …ìen geddi e leeferaaku, si wanaa halkagol e hayrugol."
